{
  "stem": "20035.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Naturally, we knew right away, once we are in Budapest, where we are.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But we still had no idea what's going to happen to us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And suddenly, he stopped right in the middle of-- that was a big square in front of the main railroad station.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he stopped there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we were sitting in the car.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He got out.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And suddenly we saw, through our grocery store, through our-- our-- our store, we had a trucker who was an independent Christian, living the same time as Bicske, suddenly we saw his truck.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And it was full of furniture.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And we had no idea if this is a coincidence or what happened.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And suddenly he opened up the door.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And with a little kick in our behinds, kicked us towards the truck driver, who we knew from-- Bert.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I mean, he was continually in our house.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And he grabbed us and pushed us, both of us, in the back of the truck, into one of the piece of furniture, which was an armoire.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And he told us that I-- he doesn't want to hear a word.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And he doesn't want to hear a noise.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And he took off.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "We trusted the man.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "But we still had no idea.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And especially you are sitting in that armoire, dark.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And the truck is going, and--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He took us home.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Indescribable.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No word can describe it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No word can describe that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We thought-- mom and dad thought that we are gone.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "God knows what's going to happen.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I mean, not only emotional, but also very difficult.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I think it was quite difficult for my parents.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because there had to be-- I know it by our action-- a huge change in our attitude.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I mean both my brother and I, in attitudes.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
